ces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n語言係fluid既, 唯一判斷用某個字啱定錯係睇你用果個字能唔能夠有效溝通<br />\n<br />\n例如你argue尐係正字, 但大部分人讀到隻字都要比D/啲load多一陣先估到你up乜, 咁你用D/啲就會更加有效<br />\n<br />\n同樣地, 而家我地屌5p字, 但假如有一日我地移晒民淨低班5p垃圾, 吾系甘牙就變成果個情況下既正字, 唔係咁呀會俾人屌潔癖<br />\n<br />\n殘體驅逐繁體同理, 雖然可悲.</blockquote><br />\n噉你將&quot;嘅啲吖嗰&quot;撻埋落&quot;尐&quot;嗰度係咩意思?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正如我係括號入面咁講<br />\n相比起 尐憨噉<br />\n嘅啲吖嗰 其實都無咁潔癖, 但同時亦有唔少人用既D丫果 (ps返, 有人屌丫係5p), 而為人接受<br />\n<br />\n我純粹諗唔到其他嚴重潔癖例子而 嘅啲吖嗰 都係相關值得討論既字 所以我放埋係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n噉你係想講&quot;尐&quot;呢啲錯字當正字嘅垃圾, 定認為佢哋同屬用正字&quot;嘅啲吖嗰&quot;嘅一種&quot;潔癖&quot;? 你一係貶低咗正字, 一係對錯字抬舉或者輕描淡寫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當初點解有人提出改啲為尐 正正因為佢地以為尐係正字<br />\n呢個post係屌緊潔癖字, 尐最後turn out係錯字我只係ps返俾人知道, 唔係我本身想討論既野 所以你都可以話我抬舉左錯字既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  理由同上, 諗唔到例子, 有無指教?"},{"pid":"925d0bc2ecc714c8400e027af890a67966522c37","tid":487815,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T08:22:59.000Z","msg":"戇鳩吓話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5defda3ed943aab08082480b8f305ff8d99ccf6","tid":487815,"uid":74278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T08:26:46.000Z","msg":"噉都唔用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如你出本字典話有咩字可以用<br />\n用其他字嘅人捉哂去斬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2321e31e5149269e2e875c24467322b3e4c99eeb","tid":487815,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢度有三種人, 用&quot;咁&quot;做例子:<br />\n<br />\n5p垃圾: <span style=\"color: red;\">甘</span><br />\n正常人: <span style=\"color: red;\">咁</span><br />\n潔癖垃圾: <span style=\"color: red;\">噉</span><br />\n<br />\n5p同潔癖怪一樣咁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他潔癖例子: <br />\n憨鳩<br />\n尐 (五毛專用, 已經證明根本唔撚係原本個字)<br />\n嘅啲吖嗰之類 (呢個還可以接受, 我覺得係個人偏好)<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講.</blockquote><br />\n&quot;噉&quot;有咩問題? 何以你歸納落&quot;尐&quot;同類嘅&quot;嘅啲吖嗰&quot;又可以接受? 係咪淨係個人偏好問題?</blockquote><br />\n#11答左, 係, 係個人偏好, 所以想睇下其他人用 嘅啲吖嗰 定 既D丫果 (丫有人話5p, #11利申左)</blockquote><br />\n你將對錯同偏好撈埋一齊有咩好講呢...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面已經講左, 其實語言係fluid既, 對錯亦係dynamic既. 如果我講得唔清楚, 我出呢個post目的有兩個:<br />\n<br />\n第一, 屌柒用噉憨既人, 糾枉過正<br />\n第二, 想知大家接唔接受到 既D丫果 (丫上面利申左有可能比較多人覺得係5p)<br />\n<br />\n希望咁樣畫出腸會清楚d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd976859d5ecf7c3cf63a78ca16ad7ef6d2f6cb","tid":487815,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T08:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇鳩吓話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就認同你既講法既, 所以想知以下例子入面既人係打緊錯字定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實班港女唔畀條仔打機真係好憨鳩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/332575/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/332575/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/search?q=%E6%86%A8&amp;type=score\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/search?q=%E6%86%A8&amp;type=score</a>"},{"pid":"6e9a52eb0343228d07a1971f2aa0e81af02c059c","tid":487815,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T09:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戇鳩吓話 <img src=